    "description": "Display free heap memory pool availability on the MCU.",
    "details": "NAME\n  free - Free heap.\n\nSYNOPSIS\n  free\n\nDESCRIPTION\n  Prints the available free heap memory pool size on the ESP32S3 microcontroller.\n\nSYSTEM ARCHITECTURE\n  Fetches '/api/status' via HTTP, which calls the native ESP-IDF function 'esp_get_free_heap_size()'. See also web_api(7).\n\nEXIT CODES\n  0\n    Success.\n  1\n    Network error.\n\nCONFORMING TO\n  NucleoOS extension compatible with POSIX.\n\nAUTHOR\n  NucleoOS Core Devs.\n\nREPORTING BUGS\n  Report bugs to support@nucleoos.org.\n\nSEE ALSO\n  status(1), uptime(1), web_api(7)\n\nADVANCED EXAMPLES\n  free"
